arguments.template:
<layout-default [options]="options" [asideUser]="asideUserTpl" [content]="contentTpl">
    <ng-container *ngFor="let item of navItems$ | async; trackBy: trackByFn">

        <layout-default-header-item [direction]="item?.data?.direction || 'right'">
            <ng-container [ngComponentOutlet]="item.component">
            </ng-container>
        </layout-default-header-item>

    </ng-container>
    <ng-template #asideUserTpl>

    </ng-template>
    <ng-template #contentTpl>
        <router-outlet></router-outlet>
    </ng-template>
</layout-default>
